      "text": [
        " قَالَ التَّوَاضُعُ أَنْ تُعْطِيَ النَّاسَ مَا تُحِبُّ أَنْ تُعْطَاهُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "From him, from a number of our companions, from Ali Bin Asbaat, from Al Hassan Bin Al Jahm, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Al-Hassan Al-Reza<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The humbleness is that you give the people what you love that it be given to you’."
        ]
      }
